ot-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">JXON</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/XPath\">XPath</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/E4X\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">E4X (ECMAScript for XML)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/Parsing_and_serializing_XML\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Parsing and serializing XML (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\">XMLHttpRequest</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Voir aussi","id":"voir_aussi"}],"summary":"Cet article décrit comment utiliser l'API DOM Core (en) en JavaScript pour créer et modifier des objets DOM. Il concerne toutes les applications basées sur Gecko (telles que Firefox) sur du code avec privilèges (par exemple les extensions) ou sans privilège (des pages Web).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"How to create a DOM tree","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Cómo crear un DOM tree","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"DOM ツリーの作成方法","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"How to create a DOM tree","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"如何创建一个 DOM 树","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"如何建立 DOM 樹","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"fr/web/api/document_object_model/how_to_create_a_dom_tree","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/fr/web/api/document_object_model/how_to_create_a_dom_tree/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web","title":"Technologies web pour développeurs"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API","title":"Référence Web API"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API/Document_object_model","title":"Référence du DOM"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API/Document_object_model/How_to_create_a_DOM_tree","titl